001BA8  1               
001BA8  1               ;******************************************************************
001BA8  1               ; Shield sprite pixel data — 16x16 4bpp, 128 bytes each
001BA8  1               ;
001BA8  1               ;   Color 0 = transparent, Color 7 = dark green (palette entry 7,
001BA8  1               ;   set to dark green by init_shields).
001BA8  1               ;   Each byte encodes 2 pixels: high nibble = left, low nibble = right.
001BA8  1               ;
001BA8  1               ;   Damage progression: each level erodes 4 more rows from the top,
001BA8  1               ;   replacing solid color-7 pixels with a 2-pixel checkerboard of
001BA8  1               ;   color 7 and transparent.  Rows not yet eroded remain solid.
001BA8  1               ;
001BA8  1               ;   Checker A (odd bits lit):  $70 $07 $70 $07 $70 $07 $70 $07
